{"tid":1112282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Sammi 搬出愛巢自我封閉 情緒崩潰拒見老鼠安","createTime":"2019-04-17T10:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:17:14.000Z","uid":209554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92a920a6ad21785dad72e4035b1fcf16749983f8","tid":1112282,"uid":209554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》昨日爆出許志安和黃心穎車廂偷食事件，轟動全城，不少fans擔心Sammi情況，怕她受事件影響心情，據知「安心偷食」事件對Sammi打擊很大，未如外界所言，她並非一早知「安心」的關係，此事令Sammi傷心痛哭。<br />\n有傳她已搬離寓所，不想與安仔共處，<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雖然物業是Sammi持有</span></strong></ins>，不過她都選擇離開傷心地，有指她的情緒陷入崩潰，寢食難安，據知Sammi目前不想見其他人，亦拒聽電話，為怕Sammi抑鬱症復發，公司安排她暫停工作，讓她可以有私人空間、好好休息，據知Sammi近年熱愛做運動，從運動中釋放安多酚，令自己保持開心，同時keep住完美體態，幸好Sammi早前患膝蓋發炎，現時已康復，希望她可以透過運動分散注意力<br />\n<br />\nSammi加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飛左老鼠安啦，放過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d41968f8dde317cd58006f6e7c45991fb07a3c","tid":1112282,"uid":209554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母軟飯安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94adf3c4b6eadfb1fc150b8e10c599d6c51566ef","tid":1112282,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"上帝早已預備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1338b0c71aa6a8ac18e66ac8d356705ae92ca228","tid":1112282,"uid":185022,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"不如佢同馬明一齊,一個係好女人,另一個係好男人"},{"pid":"65195fca7e9051d6a3291fa1db49c659d2851d25","tid":1112282,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"馬明好男人 ? 邊個同你講"},{"pid":"fd56ad0821482037438ef7ed5cd41f0ebaf51f09","tid":1112282,"uid":209554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1338b0c71aa6a8ac18e66ac8d3567